n-chi jyon t-xnaq´tza´n t-xaq u´j b´a´n; te mankb´il tzaj tka´yin extzen tzaj t-xnaq´tza´n
jun yol t-xe´l t-xe´chil: N-na´n Dios qa a jlu
counter-jinx, a Harry kub´ t-ximin Liberacorpus! tuk'a tkyaqil tipin.
