muro, extzen Phineas Nigellus Black, t-xe´chil Sirius,
jaw t-sk´o´n twi´ kyi´j tq´ob´ jatumel otaq tz´ok t-ximan qa n-watl.
“Mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi nq´o´ne amb´il te jun xnaq´tzanjtz tu´n t-xi tqanin titzen n-b´inchen Hogwarts toj amb´il weye.”
