jun Horace Slughorn mas ku´xun. A Harry otaq tz´ok t-xnaq´tzan tib´
aju´ t-xu´k t-xilen t-xi´ tka´yin aju´ Slughorn tuk´e jun t-xaq, t-spik´umal,
